This template allows linking to the C-SPAN link appropriate for many biographies. This will aid in the maintenance and standardization of these external links.

==Usage==
This template should {{strong|not}} be [[Wikipedia:Template substitution|substituted]].

{{tlx|C-SPAN}}

===Fields===
The only field is the C-SPAN identifier. If it is not provided, then the first value from Wikidata will be used. If the Wikidata item does not have any {{Q|P2190}} data, or there is no Wikidata item for the article, then a link will not display.

